<p><span>[4] Carlos Moedas，Europe can build on scientificintuition，2017</span></p>
<p><span>[5] Helga Nowotny，Preserve the European ResearchCouncil's legacy，2013</span></p>
<p><span>[6] Alison Abbott，The future of European research，2010</span></p>
<p><span>[7] European Commission: Innovation UnionCompetitiveness Report</span></p>
<p><span>[8] ERC 2019 qualitative evaluation projects，2019</span></p>
<p><span>[9] Paul Rincon，Euro science looks to new council，2005</span></p>
<p><span>[10] Malen Ruiz De Elvira，Excelencia e independenciaen la ciencia，2007</span></p>
<p><span>[11] Quirin Schiermeier，Science sans frontiers，2001</span></p>
<p><span>[12] Intra-European cooperation compared to international collaboration of the ERA countries，2014</span></p>
<p><span>[13] Comparative scientometric assessment of the results of ERC funded projects，2015</span></p>
<p><span>[14] 彼得·J·卡岑斯坦，叶静译《世界市场中的小国家》，2008</span></p>
<p><span>[15] 马勇《欧盟科技一体化研究》，2013</span></p>
<p><span>[16] 金启明《2004年欧盟科技发展综述》, 2005</span></p>
